actor Creator
actor Reviewer as Global administrator acting as reviewer/moderator
actor TenantUser as Authenticated catalog consumer
participant UI as React MarketplacePage
participant Tenant as Auth and tenant middleware
participant Market as Marketplace routes
participant Validate as Submission/manifest/validation services
participant Review as Review/moderation service
participant Quota as Plan/quota service
participant FS as Local Marketplace artifact storage
participant DB as PostgreSQL

rect rgb(238, 247, 255)
    Note over Creator,DB: Creator request and verification [IMPLEMENTED]
    Creator->>UI: Submit creator slug, display name, bio, and support email
    UI->>Tenant: POST /api/marketplace/creator
    Tenant->>Market: Claims and selected TenantContext
    Market->>DB: Ensure user is active
    Market->>Validate: Validate creator profile
    alt Profile invalid
        Market-->>UI: Validation errors
    else Profile valid
        Market->>DB: UPSERT marketplace_creators; new/rejected request becomes pending
        Market->>DB: Record marketplace.creator.request audit for selected organization
        Market-->>UI: Pending creator profile
    end

    Reviewer->>UI: Set creator verification state
    UI->>Tenant: PATCH /api/marketplace/creators/{creator_id}/verification
    Tenant->>Market: Global Claims plus selected TenantContext
    Market->>Market: Require global admin; validate pending/approved/suspended/rejected
    Market->>DB: UPDATE creator status, notes, verifier, and verified_at
    Market->>DB: Record marketplace.creator.verify audit for selected organization
    Market-->>UI: Updated creator profile
    Note over Market,DB: Creator state update and audit are separate writes [PARTIAL]
end

rect rgb(238, 255, 242)
    Note over Creator,DB: Listing creation and submission [IMPLEMENTED]
    Creator->>UI: Create listing metadata
    UI->>Tenant: POST /api/marketplace/listings
    Tenant->>Market: Claims and TenantContext
    Market->>DB: Require creator profile owned by current user
    Market->>Validate: Validate product type, metadata, pricing, URLs, and screenshots
    Market->>DB: INSERT marketplace_listings status=draft
    Market->>DB: Record marketplace.listing.create audit separately
    Market-->>UI: Draft listing
    Note over Market,Creator: Listing creation does not require approved creator status; public submission does

    Creator->>UI: Submit listing for review
    UI->>Tenant: POST /api/marketplace/listings/{listing_id}/submit
    Tenant->>Market: Claims and TenantContext
    Market->>DB: Load creator-owned listing and creator status
    Market->>Validate: Require approved creator and complete review metadata
    Note over Market,DB: submit_listing does not require the current listing status to be draft/changes_requested [PARTIAL]
    alt Creator not approved or listing incomplete
        Market-->>UI: Validation error
    else Submission metadata valid
        Market->>DB: UPDATE listing status=submitted and submission timestamps
        Market->>DB: Record marketplace.listing.submit audit separately
        Market-->>UI: Submitted listing
    end
end

rect rgb(250, 248, 255)
    Note over Creator,DB: Version/package upload, validation, and submission [IMPLEMENTED]
    Creator->>UI: Select ZIP and provide manifest JSON
    UI->>Tenant: POST /api/marketplace/listings/{listing_id}/versions/upload multipart
    Tenant->>Market: Claims and TenantContext
    Market->>DB: Load creator-owned listing and creator status
    Market->>Validate: Require approved creator and complete listing metadata
    Note over Market,DB: upload_listing_version does not reject based on the current listing status [PARTIAL]
    Market->>Market: Parse manifest field as JSON object and read file bytes
    Note over Market,Validate: Manifest is supplied as a multipart field; it is not extracted from the ZIP [IMPLEMENTED]
    Market->>Validate: Check manifest type matches listing and package size is 1..50 MiB
    alt Multipart/manifest/type/size validation fails
        Market-->>UI: Validation error before artifact write
    else Upload preflight succeeds
        Market->>Validate: Read manifest.version
        Market->>Validate: Compute lowercase SHA-256 checksum
        Market->>Validate: Generate creator/listing/version/checksum object key
        Market->>FS: Persist ZIP under local upload_dir object-key path
        Market->>Quota: Load selected organization's current plan slug
        Quota->>DB: Read organization subscription and plan
        Market->>Validate: evaluate_marketplace_package in process
        Validate->>Validate: Inspect ZIP central directory and file paths
        Validate->>Validate: Validate manifest, product type, permissions, entry points, assets, dependencies
        Validate->>Validate: Security scan forbidden/executable/risky content
        Validate->>Validate: Calculate Zinhar version, feature, and active-plan compatibility
        alt Static errors or high/critical security risk
            Validate-->>Market: version=blocked, submission=blocked with persisted reports
        else Passed/warning and low/medium risk
            Validate-->>Market: version=submitted, submission=queued with persisted reports
        end
        critical Version, submission, and listing transaction [IMPLEMENTED]
            Market->>DB: BEGIN
            Market->>DB: INSERT marketplace_versions with artifact metadata and reports
            Market->>DB: INSERT marketplace_submissions
            Market->>DB: UPDATE listing submitted or blocked
            Market->>DB: COMMIT
        option Database insert/commit fails
            Note over FS,DB: Persisted artifact is not removed; orphan cleanup is missing [DECISION REQUIRED] AMB-015
            Market-->>UI: Mapped database error
        end
        Market->>DB: Record marketplace.version.submit audit after commit
        alt Audit fails
            Note over Market,DB: Version/submission remain committed [PARTIAL]
            Market-->>UI: Mapped audit error
        else Audit succeeds
            Market-->>UI: Version and submission reports
        end
    end
end

rect rgb(255, 252, 238)
    Note over Reviewer,DB: Review decision [IMPLEMENTED]
    Reviewer->>UI: Open review queue
    UI->>Tenant: GET /api/marketplace/review/queue
    Tenant->>Market: Global Claims and TenantContext
    Market->>Market: Require global admin
    Market->>DB: Load queued, validating, blocked, or submitted review rows
    Market-->>UI: Validation/security/compatibility reports
    Reviewer->>UI: Approve, reject, or request changes
    UI->>Tenant: PATCH /api/marketplace/review/submissions/{submission_id}
    Tenant->>Market: Claims and TenantContext
    Market->>DB: Load submission/version/listing context
    Market->>Review: Validate decision and approval gate
    alt Approve blocked/failed/high-risk package
        Review-->>UI: Validation error; no mutation
    else Valid decision
        critical Review state transaction [IMPLEMENTED]
            Market->>DB: UPDATE submission review state, notes, reviewer, metadata
            Market->>DB: UPDATE version approved or rejected
            Market->>DB: UPDATE listing approved or changes_requested
            Market->>DB: INSERT marketplace_review_events
            Market->>DB: COMMIT
        option Any review write fails
            DB-->>Market: Transaction rolls back
        end
        Market->>DB: Record marketplace.review.decision audit after commit
        Market-->>UI: Persisted review event
    end
end

rect rgb(255, 244, 238)
    Note over Reviewer,DB: Moderation [IMPLEMENTED]
    Reviewer->>UI: Choose suspend_listing, unpublish_version, or emergency_block
    UI->>Tenant: POST /api/marketplace/review/listings/{listing_id}/moderation
    Tenant->>Market: Claims and TenantContext
    Market->>Market: Require global admin
    Market->>Review: Validate action, reason, and required version_id
    Market->>DB: Load listing status
    critical Moderation transaction [IMPLEMENTED]
        alt suspend_listing
            Market->>DB: UPDATE listing status=suspended
        else unpublish_version
            Market->>DB: UPDATE selected version status=deprecated
            Market->>DB: Count remaining approved versions
            Market->>DB: UPDATE listing approved or changes_requested
        else emergency_block
            Market->>DB: UPDATE listing status=blocked
            Market->>DB: Block submitted/validating/approved versions
            Market->>DB: Block existing non-uninstalled installation records
        end
        Market->>DB: INSERT marketplace_review_events moderation event
        Market->>DB: COMMIT
    option Any moderation write fails
        DB-->>Market: Transaction rolls back
    end
    Market->>DB: Record marketplace.moderation.action audit after commit
    Market-->>UI: Persisted moderation event
    Note over Market,DB: No moderation restoration/appeal endpoint is implemented [DECISION REQUIRED] AMB-016
end

rect rgb(238, 250, 255)
    Note over TenantUser,DB: Catalog search, detail, and active-plan compatibility [IMPLEMENTED, TENANT-PROTECTED]
    TenantUser->>UI: Search/filter catalog
    UI->>Tenant: GET /api/marketplace/catalog with Bearer token and organization header
    Tenant->>Market: Active TenantContext
    Market->>Quota: Load current organization plan
    Quota->>DB: Read organization subscription and plan
    Market->>DB: Query approved listings with latest approved, passed/warning, low/medium-risk version
    Market->>Validate: Recalculate compatibility for current Zinhar version/features/plan
    alt Listing/version incompatible with active organization
        Validate-->>Market: install_eligible=false
        Market->>Market: Filter item out of catalog response
    else Compatible
        Market-->>UI: Catalog item with permissions and compatibility report
    end

    TenantUser->>UI: Open listing detail
    UI->>Tenant: GET /api/marketplace/catalog/{listing_slug}
    Tenant->>Market: Active TenantContext
    Market->>Quota: Load active organization plan
    Market->>DB: Load eligible listing, approved versions, manifest, and active-install count
    Market->>Validate: Recalculate each version's compatibility
    alt Listing/latest version incompatible
        Market-->>UI: 404 catalog listing not found
    else Compatible
        Market-->>UI: Detail, versions, permissions, changelog, and empty customer reviews
        UI-->>TenantUser: Install control remains disabled/deferred
    end
    Note over UI,DB: No purchase, payout, customer-rating, or executable install flow is represented because it is not implemented
end
